<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.1">
<l>irakka miṉṟiyeṅ kōṉceyta tīmai yimmai yēyemak keytiṟṟuk kāṇīr</l>
<l>parakka yāmiṉṟu raitteṉi ravaṇaṉpaṭṭa ṉaṉiṉi yāvarkku raikkōm</l>
<l>kurakku nāyakar kāḷiḷaṅ kōvē kōla valvili rāmapi rāṉē</l>
<l>yarakka rāṭaḻaip pārillai nāṅka ḷañci ṉōntaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look! The evil which our merciless king committed</l>
<l rend="indent">has affected us in the present.</l>
<l>What’s [the use] of us speaking up to elaborate today? Rāvaṇa was killed;</l>
<l rend="indent">now who [else] do we speak to?</l>
<l>Leader of the monkeys, young prince, Lord Rāma with the shapely strong bow,</l>
<l>The demons do not call out for killing. We are frightened.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
